government has deployed two helicopters to airlift people trapped
by flood in Somali Region and transport relief.
</P>
<P>
France sent the helicopters in response to the recent appeal
from the commission for additional aircrafts to transport
emergency rations and tents to the flood stricken areas in
ethiopia's eastern Somali Region.
</P>
<P>
The helicopters have arrived in Fode, a southern town of
Somali Region, and are transporting aid from there to the flooded
areas, the commission said.
</P>
<P>
