Djibouti carrying equipment essential for the helicopters, will
also fly in aid package.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, the commission said that it has airlifted 40 tons
of soughum and 9 tons of biscuit to gode from its warehouse in
dire dawa, the second largest city in ethiopia, in the last three
days.
</P>
<P>
Part of the medicines dispatched by the Ministry of Health has
also arrived in Gode, the commission said. 
