during torrential rains which hit the area.
</P>
<P>
Florence Munyirwa, principal public relation officer of the
Uganda Railways Corporation (URC), said the corporation had sent
a team of engineers to the site to make first-hand assessment of
the accident and estimate the loss due to collapse.
