The Tamini and Saihati Transport Company (Taseco) of Saudi Arabia
decided to choose Renault among several competitors, including the
German Mercedes.
</P>
<P>
The delivery of the buses will be completed by the year 2,000.
</P>
<P>
Launched in 1996, the Illiade bus has already won thousands of
orders, half of them from abroad. 
