<HEADLINE> Chinese Defense Minister Meets ROK Visitors </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, November 25 (Xinhua) -- Chinese National Defense
Minister Chi Haotian, who is also vice-chairman of the Central
Military Commission and state councillor, met here this afternoon
with Lee Jung-In, deputy defense minister of the Republic of
Korea.
</P>
<P>
Lee and his party are here as guests of the Chinese Ministry of
National Defense. 
