spokesman said, adding that investigations are under way to
determine the cause of the crash.
</P>
<P>
Two weeks ago, an Mi-24 helicopter was brought down in a
missile attack by Tamil rebels in the northeastern coastal area,
killing two pilots on board.
</P>
<P>
