<TEXT>
<P>
YINCHUAN, November 25 (Xinhua) -- Northwest China's Ningxia Hui
Autonomous Region has spent 1.63 billion yuan on fixed assets in
telecommunications in the last five years, and a modern network
connecting the province with the rest of the world is taking shape.
</P>
