cars in the final selection: the new Volkswagen Golf (266 votes),
the Audi A6 (265 votes), the Mercedes Class A (211 votes) and the
Citroen Xsara (204 votes).
</P>
<P>
The 156 was chosen by an international jury composed of 56
journalists representing 21 European countries. 
