Minister of Finance Medgyessy Peter, Minister of Industry and
Commerce, Tourism Fazakas Szaboles and Political State Secretary
of the Ministry of Foreign Affairs Eorsi Matyas.
</P>
<P>
Hungary has been sticking to the one-China policy, the
Hungarian side stressed.
</P>
<P>
Budapest believes China is its most important partner in Asia
and highly values China's role in international affairs, the hosts
said.
</P>
<P>
