China in economy and trade, and expand it to investment, adding
that it is willing to participate in the construction of the
mid-western parts of China.
</P>
<P>
Chen said the economic system and market structure in China and
Hungary have both changed profoundly, traditional trading methods
could not suit the new situation, and it is necessary to find new
ways.
</P>
<P>
As major players in the market economy, Chen said, the
enterprises of both sides must take into account technology,
quality, price and other factors and constantly improve their
competitiveness on the market, so as to seek new opportunities.
</P>
<P>
Chen said Chinese enterprises are striving to achieve this
goal, and the Chinese government would actively support the
cooperation explored by the enterprises of both sides for mutual
benefit.
</P>
<P>
